<h3>Welcome to Can Admin</h3>

<p>
  Can Admin is a modern front end data administration component library built on
  CanJS and styled with SpectreCSS.
  It features a highly flexible and modular set of tools to enable the management
  of any type of data.
</p>

<div class="divider clearfix"></div>
<br>

