<h4>Technology Used</h4>
<p>
    Can Admin uses some cutting edge libraries to balance performance, application maintainability, and user requirements. All softare dependencies are free and open source. While python (Flask) is used to power this demo, Can Admin is designed to work with
    any server backend.
</p>

